text:
This one...
is probably for Natsuha-san!

And... this one is for Rinze-san...
and this is for Juri-chan, and the last one is for Choco-senpai!

Wow, that's amazing.
You got them all right.
Oh... so the last one left is...

Yeah, that's right.
It's Kaho's costume... Kaho's new costume.

Oh, huh!
Um... isn't it for dry cleaning...?

Haha, the prank worked perfectly...!
Can you try it on for a moment?

─ !!
Sure, I'd like to try it on!
